message.content:
1. The C-peptide area under the curve was measured from baseline to week 24.
2. The etanercept group showed a 39% increase in the C-peptide area under the curve.
3. The placebo group showed a 20% decrease in the C-peptide area under the curve.
4. The difference in the percent change in C-peptide area under the curve between the etanercept group and the placebo group is statistically significant (P < 0.05).
